  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Participation Certificates</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio1717da531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Participation Certificates</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n\n<p class=\"p\">Since the composition of participation certificates can vary considerably, they do\nnot have a specific product category. You define a product type that suits the type\nof participation certificate you want to represent. You can choose from the\nfollowing specific product category structures: </p>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper tablenoborder\"><table summary=\"\" class=\"table\" frame=\"border\" border=\"1\" rules=\"all\"><colgroup><col width=\"16.666666666666668%\"><col width=\"16.666666666666668%\"><col width=\"16.666666666666668%\"><col width=\"16.666666666666668%\"><col width=\"16.666666666666668%\"><col width=\"16.666666666666668%\"></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Product Category</span>\n</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Name</span>\n</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Unit-Quoted</span>\n</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Percentage-Quoted</span>\n</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Conditions</span>\n</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Reference</span>\n</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">010 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Stock </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">020 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Investment Certificate </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">030 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Subscription Right </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">040 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Bond </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">060 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Warrant Bond </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">070 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"> Convertible Bond </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">111 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Index Warrant </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">112 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Equity Warrant</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">113 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Currency Warrant</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">114 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Bond Warrant</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">160 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">Shareholding</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Notation:X= Function is supported</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">It is conceivable that you define two different product types for participation\ncertificates. You may define one with product category <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">010</span>\n(<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Stock</span>), and another with product category\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">040</span> (<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Bond</span>). </p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"loio1717da531198434de10000000a174cb4__ol_zsy_rwk_k3b\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Create one or more product types for the participation certificates in\nCustomizing for the securities area. </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Create a class.</p></li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">See also:</span>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4daed06542326636e10000000a42189b.html\">Manage Securities Classes</a></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">For more information about defining product types, see the Customizing activity <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Define Product Types</span> in\nthe securities area.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}